    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows three identical spheres on stands. The spheres are labeled, Sphere X with a charge of positive 3 nanocoulombs, Sphere Y with a charge of negative 1 nanocoulomb, and Sphere Z with a charge of positive 3 nanocoulombs, respectively. A note states that the figure is not drawn to scale.\" src=\"/images/1ec1b7b9133c4bbc369aa493810a2570.svg\"></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Three identical conducting spheres are on insulating stands, as shown in the figure. The spheres are far enough apart that they have no effect on each other when they are at the positions shown. Initially, the spheres have the charges indicated in the figure.</p><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">In Process <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span>, Sphere <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">X</mi></math></span></span> is moved toward and briefly touches Sphere <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Y</mi></math></span></span>, then moved toward and briefly touches Sphere <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Z\"><math alttext=\"Z\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Z</mi></math></span></span>, and finally returned to its initial position. After Process <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> the charge on Sphere <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">X</mi></math></span></span> is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Q sub 1\"><math alttext=\"Q sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span>. In Process <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> the spheres are given the same initial charge values indicated in the figure. Sphere <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">X</mi></math></span></span>  is moved toward and briefly touches Sphere <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Z\"><math alttext=\"Z\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Z</mi></math></span></span>, then moved toward and briefly touches Sphere <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Y</mi></math></span></span>, and is again returned to its initial position. After Process <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> the charge on Sphere <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">X</mi></math></span></span> is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Q sub 2\"><math alttext=\"Q sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>Q</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span>. Which of the following relations for <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Q sub 1\"><math alttext=\"Q sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Q sub 2\"><math alttext=\"Q sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>Q</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span> is correct?</p>\n",
